global blastn_report
blastn_method.metadata = geneseekr.run_blast(metadata=blastn_method.
    metadata, analysistype=blastn_method.analysistype, program=
    blastn_method.program, outfmt=blastn_method.outfmt, evalue=
    blastn_method.evalue, num_threads=blastn_method.cpus)
blastn_report = os.path.join(var.reportpath,
    '2018-SEQ-0552_blastn_resfinder.tsv')
assert os.path.isfile(blastn_report)
